content.name: amazonS3Trigger
content.yaml:
trigger:
    name: amazonS3Trigger
    identifier: amazonS3Trigger
    enabled: true
    tags: {}
    orgIdentifier: default
    projectIdentifier: s3
    pipelineIdentifier: testPipeline_Cypress
    source:
        type: Artifact
        spec:
            stageIdentifier: s1
            type: AmazonS3
            spec:
                bucketName: tdp-tdp1-vzx7j8k9faso
                filePathRegex: testRegex
                eventConditions: []
            artifactRef: primary
    inputYaml: |
        pipeline:
            identifier: testPipeline_Cypress
            stages:
                - stage:
                      identifier: s1
                      type: Deployment
                      spec:
                          serviceConfig:
                              serviceDefinition:
                                  type: ServerlessAwsLambda
                                  spec:
                                      artifacts:
                                          primary:
                                              type: AmazonS3
                                              spec:
                                                  bucketName: tdp-tdp1-vzx7j8k9faso
                                                  filePathRegex: testRegex

content.name: jenkinsTrigger
content.yaml:
trigger:
    name: jenkinsTrigger
    identifier: jenkinsTrigger
    enabled: true
    tags: {}
    orgIdentifier: default
    projectIdentifier: defaultproject
    pipelineIdentifier: testPipeline_Cypress
    source:
        type: Artifact
        spec:
            stageIdentifier: jenkinsTrigger
            type: Jenkins
            spec:
                build: <+trigger.artifact.build>
                eventConditions: []
            artifactRef: primary
    inputYaml: |
        pipeline:
            identifier: testPipeline_Cypress
            stages:
                - stage:
                      identifier: jenkinsTrigger
                      type: Deployment
                      spec:
                          serviceConfig:
                              serviceDefinition:
                                  type: ServerlessAwsLambda
                                  spec:
                                      artifacts:
                                          primary:
                                              type: Jenkins
                                              spec:
                                                  build: <+trigger.artifact.build>
